<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-8 col-lg-6 px-auto mx-auto d-flex align-items-end justify-content-center" style="height:250px; width:100%;">
      <h2 class="font-weight-bold">クエストクリアおめでとう！</h2>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-8 col-lg-6 px-auto mx-auto d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
      <h5><strong class="text-center">10ポイント獲得</strong></h5>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-8 col-lg-6 px-auto mx-auto d-flex align-items-start justify-content-center">
      <p>この調子で頑張っていこう！</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-8 col-lg-6 px-auto mx-auto font-weight-bold d-flex align-items-end justify-content-center" style="height:200px; width:100%;">
      <td class="text-right text-nowrap p-0"><u>獲得経験値</td>
